{"tid":1537421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［人手置頂］星期五晚遮打集會！","createTime":"2019-09-04T02:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T15:57:52.000Z","uid":142903,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fc4a81758554d836536d8d31f9be425f4526d07c","tid":1537421,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXRoa1Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXRoa1Y.jpg&h=7f566e06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n9月6日 「反濫捕 抗威權」集會<br />\n日期：9月6日 <br />\n時間：7:30pm<br />\n地點：遮打花園（正申請不反對通知書）<br />\n<br />\n再傷心 再失望 為自由 我堅持<br />\n<br />\n自六月九日反送中示威浪潮開始，不少社會及政治組織職工、議員助理曾經有機會出現在衝突現場。出現在現場，並非一定有參與衝突，而更多是履行職責，如協助議員工作、緩衝警察與示威者衝突、協助支援被捕人仕等。但警方多次以阻差辦公等理由，向社會及政治組織職工作出暴力對待，甚至無理拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n本會明白警察亦只是在政府無視龐大民意下的工具，但政治問題政治解決，政府即使用更大的警察武力驅散拘捕乃至暴打被捕者，仍不可能驅走香港市民追逐自由民主平等的決心。作為社會及政治組織從業員，我們有更大的責任，走到衝突前沿。同工們當中都可能害怕警方無情的暴力，都可能對警方無止境的暴力感到失望。<br />\n<br />\n我們決不向白色恐怖低頭。同工為了香港人的自由無畏無懼，堅守崗位。雖然我們面對無情的政權，本會仍希望可以為同路同工打氣，抗威權，反警暴。<br />\n<br />\n九月六日，晚上七時半，遮打花園，不見不散。<br />\n(不反對通知書申請中，如不獲不反對通知書，本會會取消活動)<br />\n<br />\n集會物資方面我地希望眾籌，有望大家可以支持下︰ <br />\n扣除眾籌平台行政費後，多咗既話我地會一半捐俾「612人道支援基金」，一半捐俾「星火同盟」，撐返一眾義士，而就算搞唔成既話，都會一樣做法處理！<br />\n捐款連結：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/NoWhiteTerror906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FNoWhiteTerror906&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3MjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=7d6090a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/NoWhiteTerror906</a>"},{"pid":"d102304a60577b34c99a6bc4150d5092ad991429","tid":1537421,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:18:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d46f3aecc53be0484cf964c4f8e840ae4870d923","tid":1537421,"uid":141576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:18:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59b91d7ad52dcb8998a105cb05e1fd3f65b1a467","tid":1537421,"uid":124746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:18:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0da03f787cf0a3911fb0da1e6e85640b9e6f7ad","tid":1537421,"uid":267425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:18:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>解散警隊 刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n我屌曬你地老母快啲推第六大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fLDFcUN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfLDFcUN.jpg&h=350c6ca1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3126317cb03f70b819f4ef43528ba1e86e960ada","tid":1537421,"uid":262125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:22:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7167ff496801cf1bb9587adf2fe8ea76e3542c8f","tid":1537421,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqNCcpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqNCcpj.jpg&h=145b357e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7ba6a3fa65bb072c87dc596c26d262cbcf774b4a","tid":1537421,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:22:57.000Z","msg":"點解無人講架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25deb906c5a0f20249594193961157b83cfb1a74","tid":1537421,"uid":111982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"【Google 廣告】上線啦 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535377</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請多多關注 比下意見"},{"pid":"b58ec1fd6a909d3d6f6efcdf4ee69e962f548735","tid":1537421,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民抗爭，長久戰、拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪、減少淘寶<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點咆哮！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtest #Chinazi<br />\n5. 不要說推，試著將呢段訊息copy and paste嚟推post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 每星期做孝子，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股、少碰中港股票<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.04"},{"pid":"d14411620063f1c276f654a5765cfd51e21ffefe","tid":1537421,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fDiRjZG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfDiRjZG.jpg&h=cb5d2da3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0q0XMn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0q0XMn.jpg&h=f1228b8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhEEtS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhEEtS2.jpg&h=c700ee1c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stbrTjH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstbrTjH.jpg&h=5810d9a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72e24dbc00c14296085784c18c23aac31ea18431","tid":1537421,"uid":229607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"pish!"},{"pid":"830a3343779e46dbe96c378e47170c3f249ba1e4","tid":1537421,"uid":278787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:11:02.000Z","msg":"push push push"},{"pid":"4e86196b1eade458cfb787f21a11e76e1bedf31c","tid":1537421,"uid":142903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:46:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44dccf64f4ce584171ab50786d036f630bb7d623","tid":1537421,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c23df6c6d67e012cd8b7481520d9daf13198245","tid":1537421,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:05:20.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"3dd0fe8c411df6158e3751188cae58d325371d9a","tid":1537421,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:07:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aed5